review_body: I was pleasantly surprised when i received this top in the mail. i expected the top to be more of a tee shirt but it is very soft and more like a light sweater. i feel the sizing is true-to-size but the design is not meant to be close to the body. for me  the shoulders and length were perfect.    this top is all about the sleeves. matador? perhaps  but it was the sleeves that attracted me to this sweater. i will wear with with a vest  skinny jeans and booties.
